The paper discusses the development of a large-scale photo tagging system using deep learning, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also mentions the use of large amounts of data for training, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper discusses the importance of selecting relevant tags for users, which is related to natural language processing (cs.CL).
